<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="puzzle-vt">puzzle <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pʌzl/    美 /'pʌzl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使迷惑：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It puzzles scientists how these creatures can survive in such severe conditions. 
这些生物是如何在这样艰难的条件下存活的，这使科学家很疑惑。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="puzzle-over-about">puzzle over / about</h3>
<p>1.<strong>苦苦思索；仔细琢磨</strong>  </p></div>